    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a great deal on a dependable ride! This vehicle is in fair condition and is perfect for someone looking for a reliable driver at an accessible price point. While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road, it still runs well and offers a comfortable cabin. It's a fantastic opportunity to own a solid car that's ready to handle your daily commutes with ease!",
