    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for someone looking for utility over perfection. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though you may notice some minor interior wear and typical exterior scuffs and dings from regular use. While the major components are functional, a buyer should expect to address some minor upcoming maintenance items and cosmetic touch-ups to bring it back to its best. It offers a solid foundation for anyone needing a functional vehicle at a more accessible price point.",
