    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and weekend getaways. It runs smoothly and looks great, honestly just a fun, dependable car that\u2019s ready for its next owner to jump in and go! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 32000.0,
