    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the S54B32 high-revving inline-six, complete with its signature individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventative maintenance has been executed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain torsional rigidity. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, currently fitted with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for precise turn-in. While the exterior displays minor patina from spirited use, the mechanical vitals are synchronized for peak performance, offering a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
