    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained example that strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is a clean, non-smoker environment; the leather seating is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all electronic features\u2014including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control\u2014operate perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is in solid health. The engine idles smoothly and delivers strong acceleration, while the transmission provides crisp, predictable shifts. We have recently performed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point safety inspection, confirming the brakes and tires have plenty of life remaining. This is a dependable, turn-key vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the 'showroom' price tag. Service records are available for review.",
